{"type":"message","id":"974af21c","parentId":"8dbd243a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:57:36.430Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问我的技能有什么。我应该查看我目前安装的技能列表。\n\n根据 MEMORY.md 中记录的信息，我已安装的技能包括：\n- skill-finder-cn\n- openclaw-tavily-search (已配置 API)\n- multi-search-engine\n- office-automation-test\n- cron-mastery\n- news-summary\n- free-ride\n- browser-automation\n- desktop-control-win\n- self-improving (已配置)\n- proactivity (已配置)\n- skill-vetter\n- memory-setup\n\n让我直接告诉用户我有哪些技能。","thinkingSignature":"1328721884482adada052cebc5bab13fbcc8babf1d4d529f24267cc4c6737b2a"},{"type":"text","text":"🎩 目前我安装了的技能包括：\n\n**搜索与信息获取**\n- skill-finder-cn - 技能查找器\n- multi-search-engine - 多搜索引擎集成（17个搜索引擎）\n- openclaw-tavily-search - Tavily 搜索\n- news-summary - 新闻摘要\n\n**浏览器与桌面控制**\n- browser-automation - 浏览器自动化\n- desktop-control-win - Windows 桌面控制\n\n**效率工具**\n- cron-mastery - 定时任务管理\n- skill-vetter - 技能安全审查\n- memory-setup - 记忆配置\n- self-improving - 自我提升\n- proactivity - 主动式工作\n\n**飞书集成**\n- feishu-bitable - 多维表格\n- feishu-calendar - 日历日程\n- feishu-create-doc - 创建文档\n- feishu-fetch-doc - 获取文档\n- feishu-im-read - 消息读取\n- feishu-task - 任务管理\n- feishu-update-doc - 更新文档\n- 等等...\n\n如果需要安装更多技能，可以告诉我你想做什么，我来帮你找合适的技能！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":64,"output":349,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":36994,"totalTokens":37407,"cost":{"input":0.0000192,"output":0.0004188,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0044392799999999994,"total":0.0048772799999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773896242493}}
