{"type":"message","id":"b385aca0","parentId":"f3e00d7f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:58:20.105Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了，在 workspace 下面。让我读取这个技能的 SKILL.md。","thinkingSignature":"89f33782f351b2397ff635a8f1b5b9463b72a21bc2b36126603b81ba4eadd03d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a4f4a4c5ckoy_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\news-summary\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1172,"output":59,"cacheRead":36689,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37920,"cost":{"input":0.0003516,"output":0.0000708,"cacheRead":0.00110067,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00152307}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773896297121}}
{"type":"message","id":"011be53c","parentId":"b385aca0","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:58:20.112Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_a4f4a4c5ckoy_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: news-summary\r\ndescription: This skill should be used when the user asks for news updates, daily briefings, or what's happening in the world. Fetches news from trusted international RSS feeds and can create voice summaries.\r\n---\r\n\r\n# News Summary\r\n\r\n## Overview\r\n\r\nFetch and summarize news from trusted international sources via RSS feeds.\r\n\r\n## RSS Feeds\r\n\r\n### BBC (Primary)\r\n```bash\r\n# World news\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/world/rss.xml\"\r\n\r\n# Top stories\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/rss.xml\"\r\n\r\n# Business\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/business/rss.xml\"\r\n\r\n# Technology\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/technology/rss.xml\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Reuters\r\n```bash\r\n# World news\r\ncurl -s \"https://www.reutersagency.com/feed/?best-regions=world&post_type=best\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n### NPR (US perspective)\r\n```bash\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.npr.org/1001/rss.xml\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Al Jazeera (Global South perspective)\r\n```bash\r\ncurl -s \"https://www.aljazeera.com/xml/rss/all.xml\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Parse RSS\r\n\r\nExtract titles and descriptions:\r\n```bash\r\ncurl -s \"https://feeds.bbci.co.uk/news/world/rss.xml\" | \\\r\n  grep -E \"<title>|<description>\" | \\\r\n  sed 's/<[^>]*>//g' | \\\r\n  sed 's/^[ \\t]*//' | \\\r\n  head -30\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Workflow\r\n\r\n### Text summary\r\n1. Fetch BBC world headlines\r\n2. Optionally supplement with Reuters/NPR\r\n3. Summarize key stories\r\n4. Group by region or topic\r\n\r\n### Voice summary\r\n1. Create text summary\r\n2. Generate voice with OpenAI TTS\r\n3. Send as audio message\r\n\r\n```bash\r\ncurl -s https://api.openai.com/v1/audio/speech \\\r\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $OPENAI_API_KEY\" \\\r\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\r\n  -d '{\r\n    \"model\": \"tts-1-hd\",\r\n    \"input\": \"<news summary text>\",\r\n    \"voice\": \"onyx\",\r\n    \"speed\": 0.95\r\n  }' \\\r\n  --output /tmp/news.mp3\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Example Output Format\r\n\r\n```\r\n📰 News Summary [date]\r\n\r\n🌍 WORLD\r\n- [headline 1]\r\n- [headline 2]\r\n\r\n💼 BUSINESS\r\n- [headline 1]\r\n\r\n💻 TECH\r\n- [headline 1]\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Best Practices\r\n\r\n- Keep summaries concise (5-8 top stories)\r\n- Prioritize breaking news and major events\r\n- For voice: ~2 minutes max\r\n- Balance perspectives (Western + Global South)\r\n- Cite source if asked\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773896300109}}
{"type":"message","id":"41c1ce16","parentId":"011be53c","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:58:27.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经获取到了 news-summary 技能的详细信息。现在给用户做一个清晰的介绍。","thinkingSignature":"8ae47f4c92fe89eca1727f2c7f7203ed469c63d4a73fe179921279c0382681e2"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📰 News Summary 技能介绍\n\n这是一个新闻摘要技能，当你需要了解全球新闻、每日简报或天下大事时使用。\n\n### 功能特点\n\n1. **文本摘要** - 获取国际权威 RSS 源新闻并总结\n2. **语音摘要** - 可生成语音版新闻播报（通过 OpenAI TTS）\n\n### 新闻来源\n\n| 来源 | 特点 |\n|------|------|\n| BBC | 主源，覆盖全球、商业、科技 |\n| Reuters | 国际通讯社 |\n| NPR | 美国视角 |\n| Al Jazeera | 全球南方视角 |\n\n### 使用方式\n\n直接告诉我：\n- \"今天有什么新闻\"\n- \"来一份新闻摘要\"\n- \"播报国际新闻\"\n\n### 输出示例\n\n```\n📰 新闻摘要 [2026-03-19]\n\n🌍 全球\n- 头条新闻1\n- 头条新闻2\n\n💼 商业\n- 商业新闻1\n\n💻 科技\n- 科技新闻1\n```\n\n### 小贴士\n\n- 保持简洁，5-8条重点新闻\n- 优先重大突发新闻\n- 语音版建议控制在2分钟内\n- 可平衡西方和全球南方视角\n\n想现在来一份新闻摘要吗？ 🎧"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":1884,"output":271,"cacheRead":36689,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38844,"cost":{"input":0.0005652,"output":0.0003252,"cacheRead":0.00110067,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00199107}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773896300113}}
{"type":"message","id":"d65c6b7c","parentId":"41c1ce16","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:59:43.338Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-19 12:59:42 GMT+8] Feishu[newsai] DM | ou_e3b34b8c8d58e2d214acbf8067cdc1c9 [msg:om_x100b548c651a18a8b4c5bdc43b00eab]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b548c651a18a8b4c5bdc43b00eab\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e3b34b8c8d58e2d214acbf8067cdc1c9\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_e3b34b8c8d58e2d214acbf8067cdc1c9\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Thu 2026-03-19 12:59 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_e3b34b8c8d58e2d214acbf8067cdc1c9\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e3b34b8c8d58e2d214acbf8067cdc1c9\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_e3b34b8c8d58e2d214acbf8067cdc1c9\"\n}\n```\n\n问题是这些新闻来源我都是无法访问有网络限制的"}],"timestamp":1773896383337}}
{"type":"message","id":"e702a617","parentId":"d65c6b7c","timestamp":"2026-03-19T04:59:51.214Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说这些新闻来源（BBC、Reuters、NPR、Al Jazeera）都有网络限制，无法访问。这是一个实际的问题。\n\n我有几个可能的解决方案：\n\n1. 使用国内可访问的新闻源 - 比如新华网、人民网、腾讯新闻、网易新闻等\n2. 使用 web_search 工具搜索新闻 - 通过 Brave Search API 可能能绕过一些限制\n3. 使用 multi-search-engine 技能 - 这个技能集成多个搜索引擎，可能有更好的覆盖\n\n让我先尝试用 web_search 或 multi-search-engine 来获取新闻，看看效果如何。或者我可以修改 news-summary 技能，使其使用国内可访问的新闻源。\n\n让我先尝试获取一些新闻，看看当前环境能否访问：","thinkingSignature":"502691b8775dc0b317f7029835426ecd6bdc7d8cf3b2b8fecbb959beed9d2213"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！BBC、Reuters 这些源国内确实访问受限。\n\n让我测试一下替代方案 — 用**多搜索引擎**来获取新闻，这个方式更灵活：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_izggm2dsoel1_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"date_after":"2026-03-18","freshness":"day","query":"international news headlines today"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":64,"output":230,"cacheRead":37348,"cacheWrite":1675,"totalTokens":39317,"cost":{"input":0.0000192,"output":0.000276,"cacheRead":0.0011204399999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00020099999999999998,"total":0.00161664}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773896383338}}
